channel.title: Warriors guild cyclops co-ordinates
channel.description: Anybody knows the co-ordinates for the place in the warriorsguild where those cyclops are?

item.title: Warriors guild cyclops co-ordinates
item.dc:creator: @Cres Cres
item.description:
@Cres wrote:

[quote=“someone2, post:3, topic:379489”][quote author=Cres link=topic=475330.msg3476223#msg3476223 date=1295725256]

Not sure if it’s client dependent, as I’ve never messed with maps…

But, Project Insanity usually has them at: X:2885, Y:5327, H:2

Project Insanity has a 317 client loading 474 content , the Warrior’s Guild wasn’t added in 317 client version…
[/quote]
Yeah, just figured that out. Now i’ll have to find another place to make my training arena, lol.[/quote]
what i suggest you do is get a 317 coords list and tele around them to find some good spots.
i suggest brimhaven , mole tunnels , desert treasure caves , those make good large places where you can make training areas
